{"tid":1687591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國又贏] 華為大量員工辭職，原因係不停加班或者上司垃圾同內部權鬥","createTime":"2019-11-02T03:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T02:00:52.000Z","uid":155095,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59614bb2f68402d234a34649f6de9f2ed65d4094","tid":1687591,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191101/mobile/bkn-20191101220855491-1101_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191101%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191101220855491-1101_00842_001.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8M0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=0ce703c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191101/mobile/bkn-20191101220855491-1101_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒統計，華為今年以來已有近<span style=\"color: red;\">1,000人離開</span>，有離職的員工哭訴「實在捱不下去了，生理預警要求離開」、「有工作無生活，身體折磨壞了」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">加班在華為是最基本的工作</span>，加班時間長短是衡量員工是否優秀的唯一標準」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/XJZWq0Y04Z0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FXJZWq0Y04Z0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c1b7fbcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了加班問題，也有員工因能力不足而被勸退，或遇到頻率不合的長官，離職的華為員工表示，「在華為<span style=\"color: red;\">遇到垃圾主管就趕緊換崗</span>，同樣一個人，在不同的主管下會有不一樣的成績。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2950550/org/664fcf9a23f3a13504016f7875dcdb14.jpg/mfxs8RC19-NpNTBFtbUjWYBW_VdealEB_g2Mif4NjIk?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2950550%2Forg%2F664fcf9a23f3a13504016f7875dcdb14.jpg%2Fmfxs8RC19-NpNTBFtbUjWYBW_VdealEB_g2Mif4NjIk%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=d3f36c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，大多數離職員工都覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">華為內部太複雜了</span>，稱「對這裏極其失望，傳說中的大平台，<span style=\"color: red;\">一團糟，宮內鬥</span>，愈來愈浮躁。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://221.179.172.81:8080/mnt_manage//ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20190220/1550642033343047789.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F221.179.172.81%3A8080%2Fmnt_manage%2F%2Fueditor%2Fjsp%2Fupload%2Fimage%2F20190220%2F1550642033343047789.png&h=348daff9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d247b0837945edb8358738c9df5d3dcbfb3804c2","tid":1687591,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890b49ff4fa4e2137eba0723e205652666aa448d","tid":1687591,"uid":224916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"華為一句話清舊血換新力軍，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbee3f969bc9cfbdc145795a72e260cb5f836f6","tid":1687591,"uid":279356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYzJAWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYzJAWY.gif&h=a0d111a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fd5392f75c7df1cf184196fe2d43b7254ab236e","tid":1687591,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"中華無為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ae88d12e38d1df2575f8d29320b893d2307b35","tid":1687591,"uid":196671,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"中國人唔係好鍾意講「螂性」同996（朝九晚九，六天工作）？咁唔捱得呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700c547bf59b7dcf7ded8b62b60b48559100bcf1","tid":1687591,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0bc2a7f9dd5122f434ae00e1794bd00766d2ba","tid":1687591